{"word":"G4026 - περιΐστημι - periḯstēmi - per-ee-is'-tay-mee - Avoid","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">περιΐστημι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>periḯstēmi"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>per-ee-is'-tay-mee"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Avoid"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - சூழ், விலகியிரு, விலகு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. to place around (one)"},{"paragraph":"2. to stand around"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G4012 - περί - perí - per-ee'/4012\">G4012</a> and <a href=\"#/G2476 - ἵστημι - hístēmi - his'-tay-mee/2476\">G2476</a>; to <i>stand</i> all <i>around</i>, that is, (near) to <i>be a bystander</i>, or (aloof) to <i>keep away</i> from: - avoid, shun, stand by (round about)."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"}]}